WEBVTT

1
01:02:10.750 --> 01:02:12.580 
玛利亚啊!
Anamaria.

2
01:02:14.360 --> 01:02:16.150 
我想你这巴掌你又挨冤枉了吧?
I suppose you didn't deserve that.

3
01:02:16.220 --> 01:02:18.160 
没有 这不冤枉
No, that one I deserved.

4
01:02:18.230 --> 01:02:20.420 
你偷了我的船!
You stole my boat!

5
01:02:20.500 --> 01:02:23.160 
其实...
Actually --

6
01:02:23.230 --> 01:02:26.030 
只是借用一下 未经允许的借用
Borrowed. Borrowed without permission.

7
01:02:26.100 --> 01:02:28.130 
但一心一意要还给你的
But with every intention of bringing it back.

8
01:02:28.200 --> 01:02:29.690 
可你还了吗?!
But you didn't!

9
01:02:29.770 --> 01:02:32.640 
我会另还一艘给你的
You'll get another one.

10
01:02:32.710 --> 01:02:33.540 
那当然
I will.

11
01:02:33.610 --> 01:02:35.100 
一艘更好的
A better one.

12
01:02:35.180 --> 01:02:36.840 
一艘更好的!
A better one!

13
01:02:36.910 --> 01:02:37.710 
那艘!
That one.

14
01:02:37.780 --> 01:02:39.410 
哪艘?
What one?

